│ Task Classification → Model Selection → Execution │
│ │
│ • GPT-5: Complex reasoning, coding tasks │
│ • Claude 4: Long context, nuanced analysis │
│ • Gemini Pro: Multimodal, Google ecosystem │
│ • Local LLMs: Cost-sensitive, offline tasks │
